Hey, we're fine. Assuming you are sitting at a red light and a wall hits 
you at 35 mph you'll be okay. It is when some sort of shaped thing like 
a truck or heavy car hits the single layer of sheet metal nose gets 
punctured that you are in trouble...

Chris in Cookeville




